cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and discourse parsing. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses a maximum entropy model for classification. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves developing a parser to understand human language. It may also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves identifying and classifying textual information. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves developing a model to improve performance.
